{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.1","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Jas.003.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">R\u00e9sister \u00e0 l\u2019entra\u00eenement des passions<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. Ja 3:14-16. (Ps 66:18. 1 Ti 2:8.) 1 Jn 2:15-17. (1 Pi 5:5-9. Lu 18:13, 14.) L\u00e9 19:16.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>D\u2019o\u00f9 viennent les luttes, et d\u2019o\u00f9 viennent les querelles parmi vous? N\u2019est-ce pas de vos passions qui combattent dans vos membres?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.2","name":"Jacques 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.3.18","name":"Jacques 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.3.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.2","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Vous convoitez, et vous ne poss\u00e9dez pas; vous \u00eates meurtriers et envieux, et vous ne pouvez pas obtenir; vous avez des querelles et des luttes, et vous ne poss\u00e9dez pas, parce que vous ne demandez pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.3","name":"Jacques 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.1","name":"Jacques 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.3","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Vous demandez, et vous ne recevez pas, parce que vous demandez mal, dans le but de satisfaire vos passions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.4","name":"Jacques 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.2","name":"Jacques 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.4","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Adult\u00e8res que vous \u00eates! Ne savez-vous pas que l\u2019amour du monde est inimiti\u00e9 contre Dieu? Celui donc qui veut \u00eatre ami du monde se rend ennemi de Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.5","name":"Jacques 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.3","name":"Jacques 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.5","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Croyez-vous que l\u2019\u00c9criture parle en vain? C\u2019est avec jalousie que Dieu ch\u00e9rit l\u2019esprit qu\u2019il a fait habiter en nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.6","name":"Jacques 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.4","name":"Jacques 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.6","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il accorde, au contraire, une gr\u00e2ce plus excellente; c\u2019est pourquoi l\u2019\u00c9criture dit: Dieu r\u00e9siste aux orgueilleux, Mais il fait gr\u00e2ce aux humbles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.7","name":"Jacques 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.5","name":"Jacques 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.7","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Soumettez-vous donc \u00e0 Dieu; r\u00e9sistez au diable, et il fuira loin de vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.8","name":"Jacques 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.6","name":"Jacques 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.8","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Approchez-vous de Dieu, et il s\u2019approchera de vous. Nettoyez vos mains, p\u00e9cheurs; purifiez vos c\u0153urs, hommes irr\u00e9solus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.9","name":"Jacques 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.7","name":"Jacques 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.9","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Sentez votre mis\u00e8re; soyez dans le deuil et dans les larmes; que votre rire se change en deuil, et votre joie en tristesse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.10","name":"Jacques 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.8","name":"Jacques 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.10","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Humiliez-vous devant le Seigneur, et il vous \u00e9l\u00e8vera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.11","name":"Jacques 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.9","name":"Jacques 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.11","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Ne parlez point mal les uns des autres, fr\u00e8res. Celui qui parle mal d\u2019un fr\u00e8re, ou qui juge son fr\u00e8re, parle mal de la loi et juge la loi. Or, si tu juges la loi, tu n\u2019es pas observateur de la loi, mais tu en es juge.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.12","name":"Jacques 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.10","name":"Jacques 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.12","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:12","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Un seul est l\u00e9gislateur et juge, c\u2019est celui qui peut sauver et perdre; mais toi, qui es-tu, qui juges le prochain?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.13","name":"Jacques 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.11","name":"Jacques 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.13","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:13","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">\u00c0 ceux qui forment des projets<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-17: cf. Lu 12:16-20. Pr 27:1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>A vous maintenant, qui dites: Aujourd\u2019hui ou demain nous irons dans telle ville, nous y passerons une ann\u00e9e, nous trafiquerons, et nous gagnerons!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.14","name":"Jacques 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.12","name":"Jacques 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.14","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:14","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Vous qui ne savez pas ce qui arrivera demain! car, qu\u2019est-ce que votre vie? Vous \u00eates une vapeur qui para\u00eet pour un peu de temps, et qui ensuite dispara\u00eet.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.15","name":"Jacques 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.13","name":"Jacques 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.15","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:15","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Vous devriez dire, au contraire: Si Dieu le veut, nous vivrons, et nous ferons ceci ou cela.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.16","name":"Jacques 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.14","name":"Jacques 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.16","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:16","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Mais maintenant vous vous glorifiez dans vos pens\u00e9es orgueilleuses. C\u2019est chose mauvaise que de se glorifier de la sorte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.17","name":"Jacques 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.15","name":"Jacques 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.17","label":"","reference":"Jacques 4:17","prev_osis_id":"Jas.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jas.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jas.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Celui donc qui sait faire ce qui est bien, et qui ne le fait pas, commet un p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jas.4","name":"Jacques 4","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.5.1","name":"Jacques 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jas.4.16","name":"Jacques 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jas.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbbdbc9d0.53815242');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbbdbc9d0.53815242\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbbdbc9d0.53815242","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbbdbc9d0.53815242'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbbdbc9d0.53815242\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}